snippet.title: Stramedia: my_MISADVENTURE - Overhaul Preview Teaser Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
After accepting an invitation to the tour around Stramedia Safehouse Facility, not even expecting for the acception to go through, Nathan Philips does not realize what domino chain of life changing (and ruining) events he signed himself and his classmates up for.

Stramedia: my_MISADVENTURE, finally have picked the right game engine, is going through a major overhaul and is set to look nice and shiny when it arrives to Windows, Linux (+SteamOS) and Android!

Wishlist Stramedia: my_MISADVENTURE on Steam 🞂 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1221670/Stramedia_my_MISADVENTURE/
